description.en: A card with the original format, printed on a paper coated on a face, and have its white back decorated of my signature in bottom.\nThe thickness of printing paper is 300gr and allows a semi-glossy rendering and a beautiful contrast for the colors.\nCard's size: 10x10 cm.
